Well, I had my own doubts about it, but wasn't sure whether a regressive
tax fit the bill.  (heh)  SO here is the re-proto.

Proto-PROPOSAL DB7  (Vanyel)
Nomic Taxes
(Creates a Rule)

Exactly once every Nomic Week, the Banker shall deduct 1% from the 
Mark Accounts of all Players and Groups, and any other Mark-Possessing 
Entities except the Bank.  Players who have 1 Mark or less are exempt
from this requirement.  All proceeds from this Tax shall be added to
the Bank.

***END PROTO

proto history:
1st protoed 9/20 12:20AM CDT
revised 9/20 12:35AM CDT

And, as a companion to this:

Proto-PROPOSAL DB8  (Vanyel)
Destruction of Marks
(Amends a Rule)



Vanyel


